Start
/ %!flag% (leading-! shape) must still parse as a single variable reference (Name="!flag"),
/ NOT be reinterpreted as a Property dereference of the form %x!key%. Coverage row 4.13.
/ The leading-! marker is the "infrastructure" namespace prefix (%!data%, %!error%, …);
/ the Stage-4 Property suffix only fires when the ! sits between a name and a key.
- set %payload% = 'leading-bang-still-binds'
- set %!flag% = 'sits-in-bang-namespace'
- assert %!flag% equals 'sits-in-bang-namespace'
